---
alwaysApply: true
---

All data passed between pipeline stages must use Pydantic models in `backend/models/`.

All functions must have type hints on parameters and return values.

All LLM API calls (via LLMClient) must retry 3 times with exponential backoff from 2 seconds.
On Pydantic validation failure after `complete_json()`, retry once with a fix-JSON prompt, then fail the run.

Use sync SQLAlchemy sessions. Schema via `create_all()` at startup — no Alembic until Milestone 2–3.

File processing must handle missing, corrupt, and unsupported files gracefully with descriptive errors.
